reviewText: Another gift to my aunt in Texas and her friends and they got a big kick out of this.  They enjoy Cantinflas and the funny movies he's in.  She received this Disc quickly and in good condition.

My aunt did not know that these movies could be obtained online.  This saved a huge headache, my aunt was getting ready to look for someone that was going to Mexico so that they could bring back some of these old movies for my uncle.  My uncle recently was diagnosed with Alzheimer's and dementia. This old movies seem to help him relax for hours.
